Author: wirrwar
Title: [ANN][ICO] Victortoken esport prediction platform
Body: We launched the VICTOR project, the system that allows all users around the world to safely enjoy online sports prediction games beyond nationalities or borders. The VICTOR project enables a more secure sports prediction game with a transparent blockchain based system.  Users can enjoy sports prediction content through the official platform, and the system encrypts the specific contents of transactions and link them into block form. Then the system automatically validates the authenticity of the transaction through blockchain technology.   Visit the Victortoken website at www.victortoken.io Read the Victortoken Whitepaper here: https://www.victortoken.io/whitepaperreenLink-White-Paper.pdf .  Private Sale already started (pm me), public sale over Smart Contract is about to start middle of August.
